      "title": "Clash between two protesting factions at Temple Trees, 10 hospitalised",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At least 10 people, including one woman, were hospitalised following a clash between two protesting factions at Temple Trees this morning, police said.",
        "According to hospital sources, nine men and one woman were admitted for medical treatment. Six were admitted to ward number 72 in the Colombo National Hospital (CNH). Two of them were discharged from the outpatient department (OPD) and another two patients are still receiving treatment at the OPD.",
        "The clash broke out at 2.45 am today. (Darshana Sanjeewa Balasuriya)"
      ],
